body_html: We're working on a new contrib/summary/ package that's going to be the future. This system is already in place and works with tf.cond by design. However it's still under active development and not API stable. Eventually it's going to be moved to tb.summary (i.e. tensorboard.summary) and will yield numerous other benefits such as database support and performance.
